data.description: Splish Splash! This single story POOL home is ready to impress.  3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms and 2,125 square feet. Formal living and dining rooms with separate family room off of the kitchen. Eat in nook area and quick access outside to the private backyard. Low maintenance landscape and stunning pool and spa.  Huge side yard for more entertaining, pets, storage or patio seating. RV Parking! You choose! Corner lot offers tons of privacy.  Inside laundry room and 2 car attached garage! Welcome Home!
